{"id": "work_2b9affc1-0204-55c1-9cf6-18dc6ecef8c3", "title": "Quantum Back-Action of an Individual Variable-Strength Measurement", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1062466993"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:50.702815", "abstract": "Measuring a quantum system can randomly perturb its state. The strength and nature of this back-action depend on the quantity that is measured. In a partial measurement performed by an ideal apparatus, quantum physics predicts that the system remains in a pure state whose evolution can be tracked perfectly from the measurement record. We demonstrated this property using a superconducting qubit dispersively coupled to a cavity traversed by a microwave signal. The back-action on the qubit state of a single measurement of both signal quadratures was observed and shown to produce a stochastic operation whose action is determined by the measurement result. This accurate monitoring of a qubit state is an essential prerequisite for measurement-based feedback control of quantum systems.", "publication_date": "2013-01-11", "doi": "10.1126/science.1226897", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1062466993?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_4f83751f-be3f-5c8d-8c04-68877afdd3e8", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_efcff76a-9f19-5e6f-bec0-51e13fce22c6", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_1fd94d71-0551-57ef-a137-4cb7d7610a41", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b9adef22-e047-5198-8555-05fc0041e9ea", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_e20185ed-5a53-5c07-8cb2-e76e31976b53", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_0fada32f-4ffb-5aac-844a-3bab85fa9475", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b0f79392-e307-52b4-bc8d-700f45704748", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_dbd1d17b-28b2-5b23-a71b-90e4d810b296", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b7f874c0-f80b-59b0-ae92-d836f62f2b84", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_f3887ae3-1997-5c7c-bacd-477f516abf7d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_9d7099b8-331a-51cd-90c8-b52b85b379cb", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_40c92d30-1e13-51c2-a6bc-692493c876ff", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_7ced97ac-1108-5195-b3a2-d664e9eb9af5", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_221a5cf0-5e73-5e2b-ba8e-2c0b66d37feb", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:50.702815"}